author: Atomic Shrimp
description:
This is a walk up an interesting hill topped by the ruin of an ancient castle.  This is one of a series of videos recorded during our week-long stay in early September at Llangollen in the Dee Valley in Wales.

Join the Atomic Shrimp official Discord server for FREE early access to videos! - https://discord.gg/atomicshrimp  
Atomic Shrimp subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/AtomicShrimp/
title: Walking up to Castell Dinas Brân from Llangollen (in Wales)
